title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 25 2022

description:
The guy elected to not send any mean tweets, President Joe Biden, calls Fox's Peter Doocy a "stupid son of a bitch." Montage of Biden nastiness. China is watching what we do in Ukraine. Funny Jesse Watters-Peter Doocy exchange. Senator Rand Paul joins  Clay and Buck to discuss the interview with us that YouTube banned, urges conservatives to leave platforms that censor us.
